info: Rating, 5 stars,  · July 2023,  · Stayed one night
rating_comment: Mr. Sazzadul is great host. As he is not present so he explained everything properly through text. Check in was easy just needed to call the caretaker in advance to get an exact location where to get off from your transport to reach the location comfortably. The caretaker Arif was always a phone call away. Only thing I missed was there were only two pillows as we were two people we need two more but didn’t asked the caretaker for anything coz we left the same day as we had to a flight to catch. It’s a beautiful cozy small apartment which is very good for two people. There’s lot of restaurants in walking distance. I would love to stay once again for sure.

info: Rating, 4 stars,  · October 2022,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: Pretty good apartment, but apparently it was not cleaned after the previous tenants. On the floor, hair, full of trash, there were some unfinished cans. The towels were just lying around carelessly on the bed and under the pillow. Shampoos spilled in the bathroom, etc. If the apartment had been cleaned before check-in, it would have been 5 stars, since everything else is excellent there. Location, microwave, air conditioning, etc. The owner himself is always in touch, ready to help not only with housing, but also with other emerging issues (he helped me out with an entry visa). But it's out of the country, so it's probably not easy to trace the apartment.

info: Rating, 1 star,  · June 2022,  · Stayed one night
rating_comment:
I had to reserve instantly, I've tried to reach by airbnb message and by direct call after reservation. But I wasn't able to communicate the host instantly.
I've waited for a hour to the downstairs of the house for check in. But the care taker couldn't let me in because their host didn't confirmed my reservation yet.
After few hours the host got my reservation and reach me out though. But then I already reserved and moved to another place to stay.
Please contact the host before your reservation for this property. Avoid instant reservation and check in.
